  "remarks": "Passport no: a) Philippines number XX3966391, issued on 25 Feb. 2015 (issued by the Department of Foreign\nAffairs of Philippines, expiration date 24 Feb. 2020) b) Philippines number EC3524065. Senior member of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant (ISIL), listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). Recruited for ISIL and instructed individuals to perpetrate terrorist acts via online video.  Physical description: height: 156cm; weight: 60 kg (as at\nSep. 2016); eye colour: black; hair colour: black; build: medium; high cheekbones. Speaks Tagalog, English, Arabic. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed on: 23 Aug. 2018",
